      "title": "The Journal of V. N. Karazin Kharkiv National University. Series Law",
      "content": "ISSN 3083-5631 (Online)\nISSN 2075-1834 (Print)\nThe Journal aims to cover a wide range of relevant political and legal issues, among them: the problems of the formation and development of state and law, laying the foundations of civil society and the rule of law in Ukraine; ensuring human rights; the fight against crime and the protection of public order; improvement of national legislation and enforcement practice; international law.\nFor lawyers, politicians, scholars and practitioners, graduate students and students, as well as anyone interested in legal theory and jurisprudence.\nThe Journal is a specialized publication in the field of legal sciences, Ministry of Education and Science of Ukraine from 17.03.2020 y. № 409 (Annex 1) are included in the category \"B\" list of scientific professional publications of Ukraine in the field of Jurisprudence: 081 «Law», 262 «Law enforcement» and 293 «International Law»."
